messages.message:
Patch Set 10:

THe commit message says that this is about -EBUSY, but your code change doesn't mention -EBUSY.... why is that?
ll_read_ahead_pages() can return several other errors.

Why not just change
  if (rc < 0)
       break;
to
  if (rc == -EBUSY)
       continue;
  else
       break;

That should fix your problem.  Why do you need anything else?
